readme:
# Hacker Dream UI Theme [![CircleCI](https://img.shields.io/badge/build-passing-brightgreen.svg)]() [![CircleCI](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0b-blue.svg)]() A simple but helpful, dark but full of 'three :)' colors theme.
For a complete experience as demonstrated in the screenshot below,
use the [Hacker Dream syntax theme](https://atom.io/themes/hacker-dream-syntax). [My Github account](https://www.github.com/xeroxyde)
[Follow me on Twitter](https://www.twitter.com/xeroxyde)
If you want to submit something to include into the theme, do not hesitate to suggest me or to fork it and do it yourself. ![Sample](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xeroxyde/hacker-dream-ui/master/sample.png)
